{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2635439, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 503013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "P(A|B)=P(AB)/P(B)\nP(A|B_)=P(AB_)/P(B_)=(P(A)-P(AB))/(1-P(B))\n带入左边不等式整理得到\nP(AB)-P(AB)P(B)＞P(A)P(B)-P(AB)P(B)\n即P(AB)＞P(A)P(B)\n对右边用同样的方法展开也可以得到P(AB)＞P(A)P(B)\n说明左右等价", "timestamp": 1633063830, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2635465, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 503013, "reply_to": 2635439, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 强", "timestamp": 1633064143, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2635505, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 503013, "reply_to": 2635439, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 这样子就能说明左右等价吗", "timestamp": 1633064521, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2636311, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 503013, "reply_to": 2635505, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 全部是充要条件，必然等价", "timestamp": 1633076441, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 132, "w": 1254}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 503013, "reply": 4, "tag": null, "text": "求问这个怎么证", "timestamp": 1633062870, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1633076442, "url": "6t/6tw4aetyakrf6q3dk2vezvd36c5iakmy.png", "vote": {}}}